<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Drawing Room</td></tr>
<tr id="L65"><td><a href="#L65">65</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: The place is stuffed full of things. A bust of Napoleon on a stand, a suit of armour, a globe, tapestry and swords and shields on the walls, an open fire, a harpsichord and a large mirror</td></tr>

<tr id="L66"><td><a href="#L66">66</a></td><td>MCCOY:  In the name of heaven, where are we?</td></tr>

